profitability and prosperity for investing in the Fund which is mainly  
constituted to stabilize and long-term development of capital market.  
In addition to that they will also taking initiative to arrange  
presentation, if necessary, for creating attraction to the NRBs for  
investing in the Bangladesh Fund.

